A cyberpunk-style visualization of glowing data packets traveling through translucent fiber optic cables that weave through a dark, neon-lit cityscape. The cables pulse with electric blue and magenta light, revealing streams of binary information flowing like blood through digital veins. In the foreground, a holographic monitoring interface floats in mid-air, displaying real-time waveforms and signal patterns in cyan and orange. The scene is viewed from a low angle, looking up through layers of interconnected network infrastructure, with rain droplets catching the neon reflections. The atmosphere is moody and technical, with deep shadows contrasted by the vivid glow of active data transmission lines crisscrossing the frame like a luminous nervous system.
